<section xml:id="s_extrema">
  <title>Extrema of functions</title>
<definition xml:id="d_extrema">
  <title>Extrema</title>
  <statement>
    <p>
      <ul>
      <li>
        <title>Maximum value on <m>X</m></title>
        <p>
          Let <m>f</m> be defined on <m>X</m>. A <term>maximum value of <m>f</m> on <m>X</m></term> is a number <m>c\in \mathbb{R}</m> such that <m>f(x_0)=c</m> for some <m>x_0\in X</m>, and
          <me>
            f(x)\leq c
          </me>
          for all <m>x\in X</m>.
        </p>
      </li>
    </ul>
    </p>
  </statement>
</definition>
